name: Congested Nightmare Carriage
description:
One of the most horrible encounters to be had in Blackhaven Institution's Nursery Wing. Relentless streams of highly acidic corrosive vomit shoot constantly out of this demon when encountered, more so than any other nightmare carriage. This demon embodies the absolute discomfort and suffering faced by those infants who were jam packed into carriages and perished on the day of the fire...
Horror painting project
